summary:
2018 - August 2020
Because of my thesis about 'Transgender individuals in Cyprus' for my Bachelor in Sociology and Political Sciences I gained a new-found interest in gender diversity. This is why I chose a Research Master degree in Gender Studies at the University of Utrecht. I have completed my Master Thesis on Gender Equality in the Political Sphere of Cyprus in August 2020.

2014 - 2018
I am an undergraduate student in Sociology at the University of Cyprus, with a minor degree in Political Sciences. My research interests focus on human rights, equality, culture, and religion.
